Titolo: Helix (video game)

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Helix is a music video game for WiiWare by Ghostfire Games for 1000 Wii Points (and, now that DSiWare has been created, Nintendo Points). The objective of the game is to accurately copy gestures with the Wii Remote to the beat of the music. The game encourages players to use two Wii Remotes to play, and features 26 music tracks from independent musicians.Helix was released on August 25, 2008 in North America and on September 26, 2008 in Europe.